          <title>Ohio state Sen. Ben Espy, who died at 81, to be remembered at service for breaking barriers</title>
          <description><![CDATA[COLUMBUS, Ohio (AP) — Respected Ohio attorney and former state Sen. Ben Espy will be remembered at a celebration of life Monday for his decades of service to the state and its capital city. Espy died on Jan. 4 at age 81 after a brief illness.]]></description>
